/></blockquote><br />\n而家諗起陣味已經想嘔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n 打邊爐落白蘿蔔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a889870af195a249b018045bda12e79990448b39","tid":418660,"uid":5375,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"白蘿蔔煲蜆正到"},{"pid":"21736d55d3f8d32150bc11feb9c457c0a5e7b5b9","tid":418660,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T18:00:06.000Z","msg":"不要再說了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4eabf383e13ba5101fb7f256780220fa6a44428","tid":418660,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T18:01:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>蘿蔔糕呢？</blockquote><br />\n蘿蔔糕我又接受到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實煮蘿蔔視乎個湯汁蓋唔蓋到白蘿蔔朕草青味<br />\n你可以試下日本白蘿蔔先，朕蘿蔔味冇中國蘿蔔咁濃"},{"pid":"fc2e98b2136469071d644b0b160655c8dfe37545","tid":418660,"uid":1627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T18:04:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>蘿蔔糕呢？</blockquote><br />\n蘿蔔糕我又接受到喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以前都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實煮蘿蔔視乎個湯汁蓋唔蓋到白蘿蔔朕草青味<br />\n你可以試下日本白蘿蔔先，朕蘿蔔味冇中國蘿蔔咁濃</blockquote><br />\n細個咬過一啖白蘿蔔，頂唔順陣味當堂成舊嘔左出黎，自此就對白蘿蔔有陰影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a749abe7